21#include <sys/cdefs.h>
22#ifndef lint
23__RCSID("$NetBSD: bpf_dump.c,v 1.5 2017/01/24 23:29:13 christos Exp $");
24#endif
25
26#ifdef HAVE_CONFIG_H
27#include "config.h"
28#endif
29
30#include <netdissect-stdinc.h>
31
32#include <stdio.h>
33
34#include "netdissect.h"
35
36void
37bpf_dump(const struct bpf_program *p, int option)
38{
39 struct bpf_insn *insn;
40 int i;
41 int n = p->bf_len;
42
43 insn = p->bf_insns;
44 if (option > 2) {
45 printf("%d\n", n);
46 for (i = 0; i < n; ++insn, ++i) {
47 printf("%u %u %u %u\n", insn->code,
48 insn->jt, insn->jf, insn->k);
49 }
50 return ;
51 }
52 if (option > 1) {
53 for (i = 0; i < n; ++insn, ++i)
54 printf("{ 0x%x, %d, %d, 0x%08x },\n",
55 insn->code, insn->jt, insn->jf, insn->k);
56 return;
57 }
58 for (i = 0; i < n; ++insn, ++i) {
59#ifdef BDEBUG
60 extern int bids[];
61 printf(bids[i] > 0 ? "[%02d]" : " -- ", bids[i] - 1);
62#endif
63 puts(bpf_image(insn, i));
64 }
65}
